        "episode_id": "ep-2a703b6f57d9020f",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Let me give you the version I actually believe. Wreck penetration is a planning problem first, a buoyancy problem second. We've seen this play out at teams using GoPro. I've watched this pattern hold across three different teams.",
